name: CryptoSerpent #022
description: Jake Faster is a racing freak with a serious addiction to the smell of gasoline. All his racing buddies firmly believe that he is so reckless that he probably will be killed in an explosion caused by the ash of his cigarette. He was a schoolmate of Lilo Beach, but their personalities clashed a lot, so much so that he used to stick his head in the toilet when he got mad at him.
